「'''Bravely You'''」 is the opening theme of the anime ''[[Charlotte]]. 
==Introduction==
The song with ethereal melody and voice {{spoiler|, ''the Great Compassion Mantra'', }}and the lyrics that were written by the demon [[Jun Maeda]] himself, seems to predict the development ofbthe story.

